      <string>Allows querying and visualizing the different territorial units of Argentina using Georef data. Select the type of unit (provinces, departments, municipalities, localities, streets, among others) and enter the desired filters to get a list of results. The matching features will be automatically added to the project as a new geographic layer.</string>
